snippet.title: Quiz Ah Megamisama
snippet.description: Quiz Aa! Megami-sama: Tatakau Tsubasa to Tomoni (クイズ ああっ女神さまっ ～闘う翼とともに～) is a quiz game for the Sega Dreamcast and Sega NAOMI arcade platform, based on the Aa! Megami-sama manga series.
